    in  l , defn-wk-⊩ᵛ∷ (stepᵗ₁ (escape-⊩ᵛ∷ ⊩t)) ⊩t
  wf-↦∷∈ᵛ {∇ = ∇ ∙⟨ opa φ ⟩[ t ∷ A ]} (there α↦t) »∇ =
    let »∇′ , ok , _ , ⊩B , _ , φ↜ , ⊩u = »ᵛ∙ᵒ⇔ .proj₁ »∇
        l , ⊩t = wf-↦∷∈ᵛ α↦t »∇′
    in  l , defn-wk-⊩ᵛ∷ (stepᵒ₁ ok (escape-⊩ᵛ ⊩B) φ↜ (escape-⊩ᵛ∷ ⊩u)) ⊩t
  wf-↦∷∈ᵛ {∇ = ∇ ∙⟨ tra ⟩[ t ∷ A ]} (there α↦t) »∇ =
